</div>

<div class="bg-body-secondary">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">6 Courts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>3 Clay Courts</li>
      <li>2 Grass Courts</li>
      <li>1 Hard Court</li>
    </ul>
    <p> All our courts are high quality and are maintained by trained specialists. Every member can reserve a court to
      practise or play a friendly game with other members.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Clubhouse:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Caf√©</li>
      <li>Bar</li>
      <li>Restaurant</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our clubhouse is a great place to relax after a match or a training session. It has a bar, a restaurant and a
      terrace. It is also a great place to meet other members and make new friends.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Locker Rooms:</p>
    <p>Our locker rooms are clean and spacious. They have showers, toilets and changing rooms. They are also equipped
      with hairdryers and hair straighteners.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Equipment Store:</p>
    <p>Our equipment store is located in the clubhouse. It has a wide range of tennis equipment and accessories. You can
      find everything you need to play tennis, from rackets to balls, from shoes to clothes. It also has a tennis ball
      machine and a tennis ball dispenser.Our staff is always ready to help you find the right equipment for you.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="container-md">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Parking:</p>
    <p class="m-0 pb-4">Our parking is free and it is located right next to the club. It is also very safe and it is
      guarded 24/7.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="text-bg-dark bg-gradient p-2">
  <h2 class="text-center" id="services">Services</h2>
</div>

<div class="bg-body-secondary">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Tennis Lessons:</p>
    <p>Our tennis club offers tennis lessons for all ages and levels. Our tennis club has 4 coaches. They are highly
      qualified and they have a lot of experience. They will help you improve your game and they will teach you the
      basics of tennis. You can also book private lessons if you want to learn more about tennis.</p>
    <p></p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Court Reservation:</p>
    <p>Our tennis club offers court reservation for all members. You can reserve a court for a friendly game or for a
      training session. You can also reserve a court for a tennis lesson.
      You can reserve a court for 2 hours which includes the time it takes for them to be prepared and maintained for
      other players. You can reserve a court up to 7 days in advance.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Tournament:</p>
    <p>Our tennis club organizes a tournament every year. It is open to all members. The tournament is held in the
      summer. It is a great opportunity to meet other members and to play tennis with them. The tournament is also a
      great opportunity to improve your game.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-sm">
    <p class="text-decoration-underline">Member Discounts:</p>
    <p class="m-0 pb-4">Our tennis club offers discounts to all members. You can get discounts on tennis equipment and
      accessories. You can also get discounts on tennis lessons and court reservation.</p>
  </div>
</div>

